"danger" : "success"); break; default: break; } }; const handleButtonClick = (e) => { const { value: buttonName } = e.target; setValue(buttonName); toggleButtonColor(buttonName); }; if (window.Chart) { parseOptions(Chart, chartOptions()); } return ( <>
